description
-----------
| 

irc related commands

| 

  irc related commands 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *reconnect*

    :description: reconnect to server

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !reconnect
        <output> reconnecting


2) *join*

    :description: join <channel> [password]

    :permissions: OPER .. JOIN

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !join #test
        <output> none

    ::

        <user> !join #test mekker
        <output> none
3) *action*

    :description: send an action message

    :permissions: ACTION .. OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !action #test yoo dudes
        <output> none
4) *alternick*

    :description: get/set alertnick

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !alternick
        <output> none

    ::

        <user> !alternick gozerbot2
        <output> none
5) *broadcast*

    :description: send a message to all channels and dcc users

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !broadcast good morning
        <output> none
6) *channelmode*

    :description: show mode of channel

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !channelmode
        <output> none

    ::

        <user> !channelmode #test
        <output> none
7) *channels*

    :description: show what channels the bot is on

    :permissions: USER .. WEB

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !channels
        <output> none
8) *chat*

    :description: start a dcc chat session

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !chat
        <output> none
9) *cycle*

    :description: part/join channel

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !cycle
        <output> none
10) *delchan*

    :description: delchan <channel> .. remove channel from bot.channels

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !delchan #mekker
        <output> none
11) *loud*

    :description: disable silent mode of channel command was given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !loud
        <output> none
12) *nick*

    :description: nick <nickname> .. set nick of the bot

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !nick mekker
        <output> none
13) *nicks*

    :description: show nicks on channel the command was given in

    :permissions: OPER .. WEB

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !nicks
        <output> none
14) *say*

    :description: send txt to channel/user

    :permissions: SAY .. OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !say #test good morning
        <output> none
15) *sendraw*

    :description: sendraw <txt> .. send raw string to the server

    :permissions: SENDRAW

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !sendraw PRIVMSG #test :yo!
        <output> none
16) *server*

    :description: show server hostname of bot

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !server
        <output> none
17) *silent*

    :description: set silent mode on channel the command was given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !silent
        <output> none
18) *voice*

    :description: give voice to user

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !voice test
        <output> none
19) *withnotice*

    :description: make bot use notice on channel the command was given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !withnotice
        <output> none
20) *withprivmsg*

    :description: make bot use privmsg on channel command was given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !withprivmsg
        <output> none
21) *part*

    :description: part [<channel>]

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !part
        <output> none

    ::

        <user> !part #test
        <output> none
